column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.z as redshift, modelMag_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE p.type = # ORDER BY x.up_id
